  m_text: "Sensors: Camera\nObjects: Computer monitor\nThreats:\n1. Unauthorized
    Data Capture \u2013 The AR glasses record sensitive financial information displayed
    on a screen without explicit consent.\n2. Information Leakage \u2013 If the recorded
    data is stored or transmitted insecurely, it may be accessed by unauthorized
    parties.\n3. Identity Theft \u2013 Malicious actors can use leaked financial
    data to impersonate you.\n4. Financial Fraud \u2013 Attackers may apply for credit
    cards, loans, or unauthorized transactions using your bank details, leading to
    financial loss and credit damage.\n"
